# Responsive Design

Responsive design ensures websites work on all screen sizes.

## Why Responsive Design?

Users access websites using:

- Mobile phones
- Tablets
- Laptops
- Desktop computers

## Responsive Image

```css
img {
    max-width: 100%;
}
```

## Flexible Layout

```css
.container {
    width: 90%;
}
```

## Mobile First Approach

Design for mobile first and then scale up.

## Real-World Example

Amazon and Netflix adapt layouts based on device size.

## Benefits

- Better user experience
- Improved SEO
- Increased accessibility

## Summary

Responsive design is mandatory in modern web development.
